---
title: "Open personal feed (Subscriber)"
---
flowchart TD
    A([Subscriber opens their feed]) --> B[System fetches posts from everyone they follow]
    B --> C{Following anyone?}
    C -- No --> D([Feed empty — not following anyone yet])
    C -- Yes --> E{Any posts from followed producers?}
    E -- No --> F([Feed empty — nobody has posted yet])
    E -- Yes --> G([Feed shown newest first])
